would I actually get to perform?

04:41.663 --> 04:43.290
I'd like to do two, you know?

04:43.465 --> 04:45.695
A ballad and then maybe
a more up-tempo number...

04:45.867 --> 04:48.358
...where I get to shake it a bit.

04:48.537 --> 04:53.099
